講曬 罷定唔罷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350591\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350591</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ff8ec0b1725394f8da293ab00a10a34de715ef7","tid":1350672,"uid":166474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5d4a23b243be0ff7789524cc485bdd52262a04c9","tid":1350672,"uid":53062,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:29:04.000Z","msg":"有線啦<br />\nnow 有錢，有線唔掂，就快俾中資吞噬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"本身轉左手之後已經係紅色資本啦，但係新聞部仲守得住，除左財經台唔可以去老細d樓盤驗樓，唔係即炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0922fd8f80b3424920fe8699280adc97b072364","tid":1350672,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:53:02.000Z","msg":"用緊now 有波睇<br />\n連登仔就仲睇緊東張西望 83台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851f8ff129996404c886b546f3d180eaf73b5a1c","tid":1350672,"uid":277147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"有線<br />\n淨係有線中國組同新聞刺針已經值回票價<br />\n如果屋企有藍絲晚晚開有線中國組俾佢哋睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}